Creating a container:
    docker create - create container
    docker run - create and start container
 docker run --name Jenkins -d -p 7000:8080 jenkins/jenkins
 docker run --name Jenkins -d -p 7000:8080 ImageName
 
 Check if container is running, paused or exited
    docker ps -a 
 To start or unpause container
    docker start, unpause
 Troubleshooting docker (check docker resources)
    docker top, docker stats
    Docker top  nameof container/ID	 â€“ check CPU, memory 
    Docker stat  nameof container/ID	
    Docker log  nameof container/ID
    Docker inspect  nameof container/ID
    Docker attach  nameof container/ID --- when you attach to our container then we are able to see the logs.
